data.description: Come see this beautiful 5-bedroom home sitting on a great corner lot! Amazing floorplan with primary and 1 guest bedroom downstairs and 3 bedrooms upstairs along with a Gameroom! The spacious open floorplan in the main living area is a welcoming space with high ceilings and beautiful hardwoods in the living room and office. The kitchen is a chefs dream with an island, SS appliances, pantry, and ample countertop space to create and entertain your family or guests. When you walk into the primary suite, you will encounter the stunning oasis bathroom that has been recently updated including an enormous, oversized shower of your dreams encased in marble tile and frameless glass, a beautiful double sink vanity, and an oversized closet.*Bonus: 5 storage closets, HVAC 21,Patio mounted TV,living room and gameroom TV convey,Ring Camera,Alexa Thermostats,Microwave and Dishwasher are 2022 LG Stainless Steel,walking distance to the elementary school, and outdoor storage building*Survey available!
